{"tid":1429237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張曉明：如果出現香港特區政府不能控制的動亂，中央絕不會坐視不管","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:50:48.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c76947f55257efe9993bbd40d76598e5d7f224","tid":1429237,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"張曉明：如果出現香港特區政府不能控制的動亂，中央絕不會坐視不管<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjVoXa0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjVoXa0.png&h=d18821cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月7日，國務院港澳辦和中央政府駐港聯絡辦在深圳共同舉辦香港局勢座談會。國務院港澳辦主任張曉明指出，香港正面臨回歸以來最嚴峻的局面，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是當前最急迫和壓倒一切的任務。<br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦主任張曉明：對公然挑戰&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;原則底線的違法犯罪活動，都必須堅決追究法律責任，包括追究幕後策劃者、組織者和指揮者的刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳辦主任張曉明：如果局勢進一步惡化，出現香港特區政府不能控制的動亂，中央絕不會坐視不管。按照基本法規定，中央有足夠多的辦法、足夠強大的力量迅速平息可能出現的各種動亂。<br />\n<br />\n中央政府駐港聯絡辦主任王志民：這是一場關乎香港前途命運的&ldquo;生死戰&rdquo;&ldquo;保衛戰&rdquo;，已經到了退無可退的地步。當前最重要的就是堅決&ldquo;止暴制亂，穩控局勢&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"f43f0a7ee6cd148df94ae40376f720597427aa2c","tid":1429237,"uid":296640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望出到張圖吸納中立及淺藍派</span></span><br />\n你既意見係好重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線要打仗 網絡文宣都要打仗<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 消除光復香港時代革命誤解 入黎啦仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/acHyeDV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/acHyeDV</a>"},{"pid":"af72010c0a601840aca1c0918b48e219faa27f0e","tid":1429237,"uid":12166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"知啦出動未呀?"},{"pid":"67a4d04e1566aa4de817f81896999e0af7ceeef6","tid":1429237,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0944737be6325608c4e9039c743e4f0a1a42101b","tid":1429237,"uid":271016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"快啲出老解黎止啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等撚咗幾個月啦"},{"pid":"2a0824e8e9f2bf2e8bc6ca536d32f363368b0885","tid":1429237,"uid":43600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"老解來了我訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6011b33df19e9338a16a0f98335383b6b86c7aa","tid":1429237,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"如果中央插手香港事務，美國绝不會坐視不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d3f9178829af3992f19863bf7430426814d4d4","tid":1429237,"uid":233520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民間記者會班友只識講出解放軍就返屋企訓覺，應該講，訓完解放軍走了咪再出來！</span>"},{"pid":"41a49ccf85766ff8bc66d95e7f1762819a932bb6","tid":1429237,"uid":6776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjzmfPl5fDjAhVFQN4KHTCqAikQjRx6BAgBEAQ&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.com%2Fthread%2F1347479%2Fpage%2F21&amp;psig=AOvVaw28IukwDWidnCVh8eCU6a2q&amp;ust=1565268526402786\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3D%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjzmfPl5fDjAhVFQN4KHTCqAikQjRx6BAgBEAQ%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Flihkg.com%252Fthread%252F1347479%252Fpage%252F21%26psig%3DAOvVaw28IukwDWidnCVh8eCU6a2q%26ust%3D156526852640278